'''Gang graffiti''' is the act of [[spray painting]] on walls in certain areas to represent your [[gang]]. Gang graffiti started back in the 1960s due to the rivalry between the [[Bloods]] and the [[Crips]] and [[Sureños]] and [[Norteños]], and continued on until the [[1992 Los Angeles riots]]. Today gang graffiti is common in many ghetto neighborhoods.
