'''Soomro''' (or '''Soomra''', '''Sumrah'''; ({{lang-sd|''' سومرو'''}}) is a [[Sindhi people|Sindhi]] tribe mainly based in [[Sindh]],<ref name="sen2">{{Cite book |last=Sen |first=Sailendra |title=A Textbook of Medieval Indian History |publisher=Primus Books |year=2013 |isbn=978-9-38060-734-4 |pages=114}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Soomras of Sindh: their origin,  main characteristics and rule|url=http://www.uok.edu.pk/faculties/sindhi/docs/soomroEng.pdf|website=www.uok.edu.pk|publisher=University of Karachi , Sindhi department|accessdate=7 September 2015}}</ref> parts of [[Punjab, Pakistan|Punjab]] bordering Sindh and in  [[Balochistan]], Pakistan.

